text: Yury Dudarev (born 13 February 1970) is a Soviet ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill and large hill events at the 1992 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:Soviet male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of the Unified Team Category:Ski jumpers at the 1992 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
